<strong>A1:</strong> The textbook covers various topics, including: Introduction to Medical Laboratory Technology, Clinical Biochemistry, Clinical Microbiology, Hematology, Blood Banking, Immunology and Serology, Molecular Diagnostics, and Quality Control in the Medical Laboratory.</p>
